{"tid":1473926,"cid":33,"subCid":0,"title":"［文宣組請入！］內地人好奇香港抗爭成功後會點","createTime":"2019-08-15T03:50:33.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-15T07:56:38.000Z","uid":160116,"like":38,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":15,"replies":[{"pid":"86836d1397aef36e0026fc82a0fbe07be3a2c992","tid":1473926,"uid":160116,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-15T03:50:33.000Z","msg":"經小妹一番解釋後，牆內既朋友由<br />\n1。譴責示威者暴力》了解背後因由明白示威者在不斷嘗試、警察濫暴及示威者自衛<br />\n2。政治很髒，不應禍及無辜市民》所有行動有預先提早公布、市民及記者被警察打、機管局或企圖引發衝突、暴徒是警察假扮<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/2dX0wpJ.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F2dX0wpJ.png&h=e2a768e8&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">但睇黎，佢地唔知抗爭成功可能有咩改變。最緊要係香港人一直忍受緊啲乜野。<br />\n<br />\n所以，我建議文宣組可以用對比圖，係唔同方面分析before after。<br />\n</span></span><br />\n<br />\n目的：一黎解釋比其他人知甚至係藍絲、港豬，二黎鼓舞下自己人，有成功既景象刺激大家堅持。<br />\n<br />\n內容：<br />\n1。民生問題：醫療（床位不足）、教育（國民教育）、房屋（樓價高企）、社會（水貨客、屯門大媽）等<br />\n2。經濟問題：國際金融中心地位下降（中共蠶食一國兩制，外商憂心及撒資）、銀行業爛帳危機？（hsbc)<br />\n<br />\n做法：<br />\n1。Brainstorm唔同問題，<br />\n2。揀出最重要、最能激發同理心既、同最能顯示港共賣港既，<br />\n3。每個問題對應寫出最好既改變<br />\n4。最緊要標題/內容要highlight大家唔係搞港獨，係為自己為香港<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">歡迎大家一齊brainstorm!！<br />\n<br />\n光復香港 時代革命</span></span>"},{"pid":"7d9f4ce90c21e2542ac587245e9360c291fb146b","tid":1473926,"uid":160116,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-15T03:54:08.000Z","msg":"每個問題唔洗太詳盡，有數字顯示更好<br />\n<br />\n例如：<br />\n內地孕婦來港分娩，醫院床位不足<br />\n平均一個護士對幾多人/一間病房逼幾多床"},{"pid":"6d5f67b23517ba879205c2886e2b0c25552d275e","tid":1473926,"uid":267342,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-15T03:54:21.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c8db79461946dec0e9fb8359b2404fca3cc5ff5f","tid":1473926,"uid":160116,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-15T03:56:10.000Z","msg":"或者可以整幾張連環圖<br />\n<br />\n第一張：問題<br />\n第二張：因由/原因<br />\n第三張：解決方案（而家既行動）<br />\n第四張：成功既改變"},{"pid":"7ed560950c539eda2b6d7d9375880bcda117b5a5","tid":1473926,"uid":171992,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-15T03:56:34.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://i.lihkg.com/540/https://na.cx/i/6yR8ycR.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi.lihkg.com%2F540%2Fhttps%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F6yR8ycR.jpg&h=a587efad&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://i.lihkg.com/540/https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2019/08/14/141044_b70c4022f89dcf5617302fe3f20434af.jpeg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi.lihkg.com%2F540%2Fhttps%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2019%2F08%2F14%2F141044_b70c4022f89dcf5617302fe3f20434af.jpeg&h=b7bac505&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://i.lihkg.com/540/https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2019/08/14/141056_6689ba9867dc55e5e3b796d75180758d.jpeg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi.lihkg.com%2F540%2Fhttps%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2019%2F08%2F14%2F141056_6689ba9867dc55e5e3b796d75180758d.jpeg&h=42f5c084&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://i.lihkg.com/540/https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2019/08/14/141101_1e69ec3ac35774384c7044962c18e307.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi.lihkg.com%2F540%2Fhttps%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2019%2F08%2F14%2F141101_1e69ec3ac35774384c7044962c18e307.png&h=4a3dc024&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://i.lihkg.com/540/https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2019/08/14/141106_a064336a869290c4a85c50e2c5342faf.jpeg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi.lihkg.com%2F540%2Fhttps%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2019%2F08%2F14%2F141106_a064336a869290c4a85c50e2c5342faf.jpeg&h=42d70b2e&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"993ee310d8f81e6c8bd57a0cb4a9a3dffff67c4b","tid":1473926,"uid":160116,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"20